# ---- Runtime artifacts generated by running the CLI projects ----
# (Project 3 / Project 6 write a local encrypted vault; Project 5 writes
# log/alert files at runtime — none of these should ever be committed,
# both for repo cleanliness and because they can contain locally-entered
# secrets during testing.)
vault.dat
watched.log
alerts.log
*.local.log

